<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>put one’s best face on • put one’s face on</xh5><p> <i>put one’s best face on—</i>assume as pleasant an appearance or manner as possible: She was not a very gracious person but before her aunt Matilda she always <u>put her best face on</u>.</p><p> <i>put one’s face on</i>—(coll.) put on make-up: I’ve got to go upstairs and <u>put my face on</u>, very quickly.</p> </entry>
